Package edu.utah.cdmcc.dao

This package contains data access object code to protect the programmer from details about Hibernate, SQL, JDBC, etc.

Interface Summary
IGenericDAO<T,ID extends Serializable>  
IPatientDAO This interface describes how patient addition, deletion, and other CRUD functions are handled.
 

Class Summary
DAOFactory Defines all DAOs and the concrete factories to get the conrecte DAOs.
GenericHibernateDAO<T,ID extends Serializable> Implements the generic CRUD data access operations using Hibernate APIs.
HibernateDAOFactory Returns Hibernate-specific instances of DAOs.
PatientDAOHibernate This handles all patient creation routines, utilizing the Hibernate interface.
 

Package edu.utah.cdmcc.dao Description

This package contains data access object code to protect the programmer from details about Hibernate, SQL, JDBC, etc. The basic entity that is manipulated is the Patient object.

Author: J. Michael Dean, M.D., M.B.A. (University of Utah School of Medicine)
